(Corrects second paragraph to Pan said government now sets
 home prices .)  Soho China Ltd. (410)  Chairman Pan Shiyi
said the latest round of property measures were the most severe.  Housing prices are now decided by the government and “not
by me,” Pan said at the Boao Forum for  Asia  today in the
southern Chinese province of  Hainan .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
